channel.title: Dark League Pking!. not on vps yet!, server down due to updates
channel.description:
this is a new server!! this is a server based around pking/staking this server does not have much in it. WE Are not on a vps yet in the future we are going to add pk points and custom items and alot more commands atm we have -setstat command for everyone to use -men drop 1k ea, -d long costs 1m and d axe costs 2m, -r2h costs 100k - full mith with m2h str ammy in edge -cant buy some items from store... fixing soon!
here are some pictures! [URL=http://img690.imageshack.us/i/picofserver.png/][IMG]http://img690.imageshack.us/img690/9545/picofserver.png[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img97.imageshack.us/i/setsat.png/][IMG]http://img97.imageshack.us/img97/7875/setsat.png[/img][/URL] client link is http://www.megaupload.com/?d=XHYT09I3 my forums is in my signature this is not going to be a big feature server, also i started rsc servers few days ago. k thanks, New 4Ever
